  "body": "Since `get_entry_exit_effect_epoch`'s return has a `+1`, in `update_validator_registry` \r\n\r\nShould:\r\n`if validator.activation_epoch > get_entry_exit_effect_epoch(current_epoch)`\r\n`validator.exit_epoch > get_entry_exit_effect_epoch(current_epoch)`\r\n\r\nbe:\r\n\r\n`if validator.activation_epoch >= get_entry_exit_effect_epoch(current_epoch)`\r\n`validator.exit_epoch >= get_entry_exit_effect_epoch(current_epoch)`\r\n\r\n??\r\n",
